        "statement_id": "doc::behavior-considered-undefined.md::section:0001::statement:004",
        "statement_text": "`unsafe` code that satisfies this property for any safe client is called *sound*; if `unsafe` code can be misused by safe code to exhibit undefined behavior, it is *unsound*. > [!WARNING] > The following list is not exhaustive; it may grow or shrink.",
        "text_sha256": "5108c7e80b467053cecacbdaa6e152621458eaa9cd61f406b8a9793a439eeb47",
        "token_overlap_count": 0
